ith sector at 11-12%.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/large-private-banks-face-slower-growth-as-psu-banks-gain-market-share-greenedge-wealth-sbi-hdfc-bank-kotak-mahindra-bank-muthoot-finance-indusind-19833755.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-27T13:05:46","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"802407076764000896","title":"Indian Bank reports strong Q3 FY26 results with improved margins.\nMD & CEO highlights rising corporate loan demand from renewables, data centers, and logistics.","summary":"Indian Bank reports strong Q3 FY26 results with improved margins.\nMD & CEO highlights rising corporate loan demand from renewables, data centers, and logistics.","url":"https://sqst.in/shareMessage?msgId=802407076764000899","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-23T10:49:15","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"451203","title":"Motilal Oswal reiterates BUY on Indian Bank with a revised target of ₹1,025, up from ₹900.","summary":"Motilal Oswal reiterates BUY on Indian Bank with a revised target of ₹1,025, up from ₹900.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-23T09:08:51","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"451176","title":"Indian Bank aims for 12-13% credit growth, exceeding guidance while focusing on asset quality.\nManagement remains optimistic about sustaining growth levels into the next year.","summary":"Indian Bank aims for 12-13% credit growth, exceeding guidance while focusing on asset quality.\nManagement remains optimistic about sustaining growth levels into the next year.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-23T08:51:07","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"451177","title":"Indian Bank targets Gross NPA below 2% and Net NPA at 0.5%.\nCurrent slippage ratio expected to persist despite minor March fluctuations.","summary":"Indian Bank targets Gross NPA below 2% and Net NPA at 0.5%.\nCurrent slippage ratio expected to persist despite minor March fluctuations.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-23T08:51:03","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"451178","title":"Indian Bank ac